1. LICENCE TIERS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STARTER LICENCE
  · Grants a single named individual the right to use the Software
    on their own projects.
  · May not be shared, resold, or distributed to any third party.
  · May not be used to provide services to multiple client organisations.

PRO LICENCE
  · Grants a single named individual the right to use the Software
    across an unlimited number of personal or professional projects.
  · May not be resold, sublicensed, or rebranded.
  · Includes free updates to all v4.x releases.

TEAM / AGENCY LICENCE
  · Grants the purchasing organisation the right to deploy and use
    the Software across internal teams and client projects.
  · Permits white-labelling and rebranding for direct client use,
    provided the Software is not resold as a standalone product.
  · May be installed on internal servers or shared with employees
    and contracted personnel within the purchasing organisation.
  · Includes free updates to all future releases.

